---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Tools & Projects - CUNY AI Lab">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-cuny-blue via-cuny-blue to-vibrant-900"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\"60\" height=\"60\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"%23ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"1\"%3E%3Cpath d=\"M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z\"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display text-white tracking-tight">Tools & Projects</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OpenWebUI - Featured Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-neutral-stone mb-8">OpenWebUI</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          A key part of our infrastructure is our CUNY-hosted instance of OpenWebUI, an open-source, modular platform that provides a unified interface for interacting with a curated set of <strong class="text-neutral-stone">open-weight AI models</strong>. "Open-weight" means that the model's weights—the parameters learned during training—are publicly available, which makes these models more transparent and independently auditable than closed, proprietary systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          All models in our OpenWebUI environment are accessed through <strong class="text-neutral-stone">zero-retention providers</strong>, meaning prompts and outputs are not stored or used for vendor training beyond what is required to deliver the response.
        </p>
        <p>
          OpenWebUI supports evaluation and customization workflows that are especially useful for teaching and research: swapping models in and out, adjusting system prompts, defining access boundaries, and packaging configurations that can be shared (and cited) as scholarly tools.
        </p>
        <p>
          We maintain a registry of auditable models suited to specific teaching and research tasks, and, where data is available, we make resource use legible through energy and CO₂ estimates. The platform also supports accessibility features, including text-to-speech and speech-to-text, with additional features planned.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Features grid -->
      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-3">
        <div class="bg-cuny-indigo/5 border border-cuny-indigo/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-center">
          <span class="text-neutral-stone text-sm font-medium">Open-weight models</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cuny-indigo/5 border border-cuny-indigo/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-center">
          <span class="text-neutral-stone text-sm font-medium">Zero-retention</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cuny-indigo/5 border border-cuny-indigo/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-center">
          <span class="text-neutral-stone text-sm font-medium">Citable configs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cuny-indigo/5 border border-cuny-indigo/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-center">
          <span class="text-neutral-stone text-sm font-medium">CO₂ estimates</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cuny-indigo/5 border border-cuny-indigo/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-center col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
          <span class="text-neutral-stone text-sm font-medium">Accessibility</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Classroom Chatbots -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-neutral-stone mb-2">Classroom Chatbots</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Tools available through our OpenWebUI instance</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-vibrant-200 transition-all">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vibrant-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-vibrant-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-2">AmigAI</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">A Spanish-language chatbot that helps CUNY students practice conversational Spanish through culturally responsive pedagogy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-vibrant-200 transition-all">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-2">Course-Specific Assistants</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Built for individual courses using your syllabus, readings, and materials. Support students through complex texts with guiding questions.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Examples: Writing Process Assistant, Paratext Analysis Tool, Active Reading Companion</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-vibrant-200 transition-all">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-2">Project Templates</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Reusable configurations designed for common classroom workflows that instructors can adapt across sections or semesters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Media Processing + AI Assistants Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Media Processing Tools -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-neutral-stone mb-2">Media Processing Tools</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Zero-retention APIs for media workflows</p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="group flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-cream transition-colors">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-1">Multilingual Transcription Suite</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Uses OpenAI's Whisper for transcripts with optional translation and diarization. Supports oral history, subtitles, and multilingual research.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="group flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-cream transition-colors">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-1">Image Description</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Uses Qwen 2.5 VL vision model to generate captions, alt-text, and detailed image descriptions.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="group flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-cream transition-colors">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-1">Document OCR</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Uses Qwen 2.5 VL to extract text from PDFs and scanned images, including difficult layouts and imperfect scans.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Assistants -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-neutral-stone mb-2">AI Assistants</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Research and website building tools</p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="group flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-cream transition-colors">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-1">Agent Studio</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Supports research workflows such as exploring datasets, searching academic sources, and producing draft visualizations and summaries.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="group flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-cream transition-colors">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-pink-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pink-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-stone mb-1">Site Studio</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Helps build academic websites—portfolios, CV pages, research sites, and project documentation—through a guided, conversational workflow.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Library Workflow -->
          <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-neutral-stone mb-2">Library Workflow Assistants</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Tools that automate cataloging lookups, parse reference queries, generate citation maps, and assist in research exploration. Designed to support library staff and researchers in navigating complex information landscapes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cuny-indigo to-vibrant-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-4">Develop Your Own Tool</h2>
      <p class="text-vibrant-200 mb-8 text-lg">
        Interested in developing an AI tool for your course or research project? Contact us to learn about collaboration opportunities.
      </p>
      <a href={`${base}contact`} class="inline-block bg-white text-cuny-indigo px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-vibrant-50 transition-all shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        Get Started
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
